These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, rock, soul
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, rat, turtle
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, tea, lemonade
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the owner of the snake and the fan of folk##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | rock      | indie      | soul    |
| Pet   | turtle | lizard | snake | rat |
| Beverage     | iced-tea    | lemonade       | tea     | 7up     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, punk, d&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, amber, yellow, brown
1. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| Music-Genre         | metal | punk   | rock | d&b |
| Color   | brown    | yellow | amber    | aquamarine        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dunhill, oliveros, game
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, social-worker, pilot, entrepreneur
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the pilot is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the game-smoker is on the right of the writer##1
7. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
8. the pilot is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar      | prince | dunhill  | oliveros    | game |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Job         | social-worker    | entrepreneur | writer | pilot  |

