.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, september, october
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, water-polo, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday          | september   | january     | december | october |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| Sport           | rowing | water-polo      | rugby     | golf       |

