.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, italian, german, american
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, 7up, lemonade
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the italian##3
3. the lawyer is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the architect is between the german and the italian##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the american##1
7. the german is on the left or right of the american##3
8. the german is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the italian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality          | german      | american | italian      | thai |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Beverage   | 7up    | lemonade   | tea     | almond-milk   |

