.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, skydiving, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, french, indonesian, thai
1. the french is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the indonesian is the fan of rock##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the italian##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the thai##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Hobby           | fishing    | woodworking   | skydiving | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | reggae   | rock         | indie        |
| Nationality         | french | italian | indonesian         | thai       |

