.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, november, april
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
City: rome, prague, nizza, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday         | november    | december  | october | april   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| City   | liverpool      | nizza | prague | rome  |

