.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, green, coral, blood-red
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, hiking, magic-tricks
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, scooter, airplane
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Color          | coral | green    | blood-red | emerald    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | magic-tricks | dancing  | board-games |
| Transport   | bike    | airplane      | snowmobile   | scooter         |

