.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, rose, daisy, marigold
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, nurse, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, pakistani, argentine
1. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
4. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the security-guard is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
8. the brazilian is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Flower      | rose    | daisy            | marigold     | aconite      |
| Job           | doctor    | security-guard | nurse     | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | mexican | pakistani    | brazilian | argentine    |

