.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, marigold, tulip
House: townhouse, ranch-style, victorian, farmhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, egyptian, mexican
1. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
5. the farmhouse house is the person who growstulip##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the egyptian##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Flower          | rose   | marigold | daffodil | tulip |
| House   | victorian   | ranch-style     | townhouse      | farmhouse  |
| Nationality   | canadian | chinese   | egyptian    | mexican   |

