.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, collecting, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, russian, french, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the russian##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the egyptian is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the egyptian is on the left or right of the russian##3
7. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby           | photography | video-games        | hiking   | collecting  |
| Nationality   | russian             | egyptian     | japanese | french  |
| Sport         | lacrosse           | skateboarding | biathlon   | rowing |

