.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, canadian, italian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, azalea, begonia
1. the italian is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the canadian##3
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsaconite and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the egyptian##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Nationality         | egyptian | canadian    | indonesian      | italian |
| Flower   | aconite      | begonia | azalea | daffodil   |

