.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, journalist, musician, nurse
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, family, sports, horror
1. the bartender is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the nurse##1
6. the journalist is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the journalist is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the bartender##1
9. the person watching sports movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Job    | journalist      | bartender | nurse       | musician  |
| Hobby       | woodworking | board-games | writing    | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | thriller         | sports | horror     |

