.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, musical, sports
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, emerald, lavender
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, snowmobile, tram
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes lavender##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
8. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre    | musical   | sports    | adventure      | satire |
| Color       | purple  | aquamarine | lavender | emerald     |
| Transport   | scooter | ship        | snowmobile  | tram        |

