4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person eating pepper and the person drinking water##2
6. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
7. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
