5. the owner of the snake is between the person playing canasta and the person playing billiard##2
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Game    | billiard | snooker  | canasta  | backgammon           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
